{"type": "article", "id": 3790, "title": "Swatch 2014圣诞限量款", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-24T08:18:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233308oVuU35qza8KdvnEQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t每年，Swatch 都会推出圣诞特别版手表，今年他们也不忘带来一款特别的限量版产品「Holiday Twist」。这款手表采用了漫天飞雪的白色作为底色，以 Swatch 的 New Gent 款为基础，表面、表壳乃至表带上洒满闪耀的金色，配以银色的圣诞树与雪花图案，营造出浓浓的圣诞气息。如果要作为礼物送人的话，Holiday Twist 也十分适合，设计团队选用了极富创意的剪裁圆筒包装，盒子上布满红、绿、金色组成的圣诞树图案，并且附有一个由金色卡纸摺成的 3D 圣诞树。这款圣诞特别版手表全球限量发售 14999 个，香港限量 760 个，感兴趣的朋友<a href=\"http://www.swatch.com/en/watches/originals/new-gent/suoz709s-holiday-twist\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里查询可购买门店</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233306te6ySTp4E5DhQUPY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.990625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233306MBl5RtQY01FNiOb3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052333079OUFv7MlYx85Xmnh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233307K3IjuXYM7ofbArCH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.6359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}